TITLE: Defining the Basic Structure of a ComfyUI Custom Node in Python
DESCRIPTION: Creates the basic class structure for a custom ComfyUI node, including category, input types, return types, and function name.
SOURCE: https://github.com/comfy-org/docs/blob/main/custom-nodes/walkthrough.mdx#2025-04-21_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: Python
CODE:
```
class ImageSelector:
    CATEGORY = "example"
    @classmethod    
    def INPUT_TYPES(s):
        return { "required":  { "images": ("IMAGE",), } }
    RETURN_TYPES = ("IMAGE",)
    FUNCTION = "choose_image"
```

