TITLE: Demonstrating tensor shape manipulation in Python
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows how to manipulate tensor shapes using squeeze, unsqueeze, and reshape operations. It demonstrates the use of None for dimension insertion and -1 for automatic dimension calculation.
SOURCE: https://github.com/comfy-org/docs/blob/main/custom-nodes/backend/tensors.mdx#2025-04-21_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: python
