SOURCE: https://github.com/comfy-org/docs/blob/main/README.md#2025-04-21_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: json
CODE:
```
  "navigation": {
    "languages": [
      {
        "language": "en",
        "groups": [
              {
                "group": "Get Started",
                "pages": [
                  "get_started/introduction",
                ...
                ]
              },
            ...
        ]
      },
      {
        "language": "cn",
         "groups": [
              {
                "group": "",
                "pages": [
                  "zh-CN/get_started/introduction",
                  ...
                ]
              }
            ]
      }
    ]
    ...
  }
```

